WEBVTT

NOTE Skit 9: The Fish Slapping Dance

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
[CAPTION] And now, the Fish Slapping Dance.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:16.000
[ACTION] Quayside. John stands still; Michael capers with two tiny fish, slapping John's cheeks lightly to jolly Edward German music.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
[ACTION] Music ends; John produces a huge fish and wallops Michael; Michael falls into the water.

